==English==

===Interjection===
'''[[what]]'s [[up]]?'''
#{{idiom}} [[What's the matter]]?
#(''informal'') How are you?

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[miten menee?]] (2 ''informal''), [[mitä kuuluu?]] (2 ''in telephone conversations''), [[kuinka hurisee?]] (2 ''informal'')
*Hungarian: [[mizu?]], [[mizus?]] (abbreviations of [[mi újság?]] (what news?))

===Alternative spellings===
*(''how are you''): (''all slang''): '''[[sup]]''', '''[[wassup]]''', '''[[wazzup]]''', '''[[whassup]]'''

